 {"id":"franken_networkx-b158","title":"parity: reverse_view should expose adjacency mapping and item access","description":"reverse_view currently lacks NetworkX's core mapping interface. On a reversed DiGraph, FrankenNetworkX raises AttributeError for .adj and TypeError for indexing (view['b']), while NetworkX exposes the reversed adjacency mapping with edge attributes. Match the upstream adjacency-map and __getitem__ contract.","status":"in_progress","priority":2,"issue_type":"task","created_at":"2026-04-21T07:07:49.964999470Z","created_by":"ubuntu","updated_at":"2026-04-21T07:09:07.963753985Z","source_repo":".","compaction_level":0,"original_size":0}
